            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{i}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " fourfooted beasts of the earth, and wild beasts, and ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{k}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " creeping things, and fowls of the air.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(h) Here is this word all which is general, plainly used for something indefinite and uncertain, that is to say, for some of all sorts, not for all of every sort.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(i) That is, such as were proper for men's use.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(k) To see what is meant by these creeping things see Le 11:2-47.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
